Description: Limestone ostracon: on the recto and verso respectively eight and seven lines of continuous text, a duplicate of P. Anastasi I 5, 2-7.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: H.-W.Fischer-Elfert, 'Die Satirische Streitschrift des Papyrus Anastasi' I, ‘Kleine ägyptische Texte’ (2nd edn, Wiesbaden 1992), p.4, (no.39); JJ. J. Černy and A.H. Gardiner, ‘Hieratic Ostraca’ (Oxford 1957), p.13 and pl.XLIV,I.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (393759) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/393759)
